      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To prohibit Federal education funds from being provided to elementary schools that do not require teachers to obtain written parental consent prior to teaching lessons specifically related to gender identity, sexual orientation, or transgender studies, and for other purposes.</title>
